<section class="about-section py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="about-title mb-4">About Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise</h1>

        <section class="about-section py-5 bg-light">
            <div class="container">
                <!-- Existing intro paragraphs -->
                <p class="about-text">
                    Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise is a general trading entity that focuses on various sectors of business.
                    The strong growth of Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise has been built on a foundation of consistently delivering quality projects.
                    Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise has demonstrated an unbeaten track record for delivering high quality construction projects to our world-class clients.
                </p>

                <p class="about-text">
                    We pride ourselves on a commitment to excellence, innovation, and client satisfaction. Our team is equipped with the expertise and experience to handle complex projects across various industries.
                    With a client-centric approach, we ensure timely delivery and quality outcomes, making us a trusted partner in the construction and trading sectors.
                </p>

                <!-- Vision & Mission Section -->
                <div class="vision-mission-wrapper my-5">
                    <div class="vision-mission-card">
                        <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                        <p>
                            Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise endeavors to reach greater heights and by far we are committed to being the benchmark service provider in the services industry. As a company, we aspire to be 
                            reckoned as one of the towering giants against our competitors within the distinctive construction services market segments through providing the 
                            most remarkable services that are tailor made to satisfy the core needs of our target market.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="vision-mission-card">
                        <h3>Our Core Values</h3>
                        <p>
                            At Ukukhawuleza Trading Enterprise, our commitment is built on strong values that guide every aspect of our business. We subscribe to and uphold the following core principles:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Deliver the highest level of quality construction services at fair and competitive prices.</li>
                            <li>Build long-term client relationships through excellence, reliability, and repeat business.</li>
                            <li>Ensure client satisfaction by emphasizing timeliness, attention to detail, and a service-driven mindset.</li>
                            <li>Maintain professionalism, integrity, honesty, and fairness in all interactions — with clients, suppliers, subcontractors, and partners.</li>
                            <li>Foster a culture of innovation, continuous learning, and personal growth within our teams.</li>
                            <li>Support and empower motivated, flexible, and focused teams to reach their full potential.</li>
                            <li>Value the strength of relationships and remain transparent, fair, and respectful in all dealings.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


